Sometimes it crashes with this error message:
	X Error of failed request:  BadWindow (invalid Window parameter)
	Major opcode of failed request:  20 (X_GetProperty)
	Resource id in failed request:  0x1
	Serial number of failed request:  607566
	Current serial number in output stream:  607566
Occurs if the focused window is closed before it can read the property.
